  "response": "Jack Nicholson has not been seen in films lately for several reasons. One widely reported reason is his retirement from acting due to health issues, particularly concerns about memory loss. Additionally, Nicholson has expressed that he no longer feels the same passion for acting that he once did and prefers to step away from the demands of the industry. He has chosen to live a quieter life away from the public eye. Furthermore, Nicholson\u2019s advanced age, he is in his 80s, naturally lends itself to slowing down and enjoying retirement. It\u2019s not uncommon for veteran actors to reduce their workloads as they age.",
